{"api_version": "2022-08-31", "model_id": "bc2-narrative", "content": "OfficerID: oneilld, Narrative\nAggravatedMenacing\nOn Tuesday, September 4, 2018, in company of P.O. Schuler #1843, we received a code 3 r/b for a white female who was saying that she was going to kill all black people. Upon our arrival at the victim, Etoya Edward's house, we learned the following.\nEtoya was walking e/b on Lake Ave near the store at W 87th St when an unknown female who was walking behind her walked by her and said, \"I hate all niggers. Im gonna kill you all!\" She repeated this again and theatened to murder Etoya. Etoya stated that she has never seen this female before, and the suspect continued walking e/b on Lake Ave for as far as Etoya could see. She described the suspect as a short white female/late 20's, early 30's/wearing a flowered shirt, grey shorts, flip flops and carrying a purse.\nWe gave Etoya's house special attention in c/w this and toured for the suspect, UTL.\nRecorded on wc.\nPage: 5 of 5\nYou created this PDF from an application that is not licensed to print to novaPDF printer (http://www.novapdf.com)", "languages": [], "pages": [{"page_number": 5, "angle": null, "width": 8.5, "height": 11.0, "unit": "inch", "lines": [{"content": "OfficerID: oneilld, Narrative", "polygon": [{"x": 0.336, "y": 0.3912}, {"x": 2.6661, "y": 0.3912}, {"x": 2.6661, "y": 0.5566}, {"x": 0.336, "y": 0.5566}], "spans": [{"offset": 0, "length": 29}]}, {"content": "AggravatedMenacing", "polygon": [{"x": 0.3295, "y": 1.0323}, {"x": 1.6139, "y": 1.0323}, {"x": 1.6139, "y": 1.1587}, {"x": 0.3295, "y": 1.1587}], "spans": [{"offset": 30, "length": 18}]}, {"content": "On Tuesday, September 4, 2018, in company of P.O. Schuler #1843, we received a code 3 r/b for a white female who was saying that", "polygon": [{"x": 0.5039, "y": 1.3444}, {"x": 8.1172, "y": 1.3444}, {"x": 8.1172, "y": 1.4725}, {"x": 0.5039, "y": 1.4725}], "spans": [{"offset": 49, "length": 128}]}, {"content": "she was going to kill